replies.msg:
Klopp on City: &ldquo;We played there a few months ago and it was one of the stranger games of my life.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klopp: &ldquo;The red card (for Man&eacute;) changed the game and maybe for Man City the season.&rdquo;

Klopp: &ldquo;That&rsquo;s still possible that Lovren and Matip may start together, and Ragnar Klavan, who is in fantastic shape.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klopp: &ldquo;It&rsquo;s not guaranteed that Van Dijk will start every game and that&rsquo;s no problem, he should not. Even Virgil van Dijk should not play 60 games a season and stuff like that. That will never happen.&rdquo;

